caption: Table 1: Quantitative comparison of visual quality. Our approach consistently achieves the best performance in FID metric.
description: This table presents a quantitative comparison of the visual quality of images generated by CryoGEM and various baselines using the Frechet Inception Distance (FID) metric. Lower FID scores indicate higher visual quality. The table shows that CryoGEM consistently outperforms the other methods across all five datasets, demonstrating its superior ability to generate realistic and high-quality cryo-EM images.
